#. plugin:mailchimp:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "- **Dashboard**: View all your MailChimp lists with subscriber statistics\n"
"- **List Maintenance**: Identify people in MailChimp but not in CRM, and vice versa\n"
"- **Contact Integration**: View MailChimp subscription status on Person and Family pages\n"
"- **Automatic Sync**: Hooks into person/family updates to keep MailChimp in sync"
msgstr "- **Armatuurlaud**: Vaadake kГөiki oma MailChimp loendeid koos tellijate statistikaga\n"
"- **Loendi hooldus**: Tuvastage isikuid, kes on MailChimpis, kuid mitte CRMis, ja vastupidi\n"
"- **Kontakti integreerimine**: Vaadake MailChimpi tellimuse olekut isiku- ja perekonnalehtedel\n"
"- **Automaatne sГјnkroonimine**: Гңhendub isiku/perekonna vГӨrskendustega, et hoida MailChimp sГјnkroonis"

#. plugin:vonage:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "1. Create a Vonage account at https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (new accounts include free trial credit)\n"
"2. Find your API Key and API Secret on the Vonage Dashboard homepage\n"
"3. Go to Numbers > Buy Numbers and purchase a number with SMS capability\n"
"4. Note the number in E.164 format (e.g., +14155551234)\n"
"5. In ChurchCRM, enable the Vonage SMS plugin and enter your credentials"
msgstr "1. Looge Vonage konto aadressil https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (uued kontod sisaldavad tasuta proovikreedit)\n"
"2. Leidke oma API-vГөti ja API-saladus Vonage'i armatuurlaua avalehelt\n"
"3. Minge jaotisse Numbers > Buy Numbers ja ostke SMS-vГөimekusega number\n"
"4. MГӨrkige Гјles number E.164-formaadis (nt +14155551234)\n"
"5. Lubage ChurchCRMis Vonage SMS-pistikprogramm ja sisestage oma mandaadid"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "1. Go to Google Analytics (analytics.google.com)\n"
"2. Create a property or select an existing one\n"
"3. Go to Admin вҶ’ Data Streams вҶ’ Web\n"
"4. Copy the Measurement ID (starts with G-)"
msgstr "1. Minge Google Analyticsisse (analytics.google.com)\n"
"2. Looge atribuut vГөi valige olemasolev\n"
"3. Minge jaotisse Admin вҶ’ Andmevood вҶ’ Veeb\n"
"4. Kopeerige mГөГөtmise ID (algab G-ga)"

#. plugin:openlp:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "1. Install OpenLP 3.0 or later on your presentation computer\n"
"2. Enable the Remote plugin in OpenLP (Settings вҶ’ Configure OpenLP вҶ’ Plugins)\n"
"3. Enable the Alerts plugin in OpenLP for alert display support\n"
"4. Note the IP address of the OpenLP computer\n"
"5. Enter the server URL in the format: http://IP_ADDRESS:4316\n"
"6. If you've configured authentication in OpenLP, enter the username and password"
msgstr "1. Installige OpenLP 3.0 vГөi uuem oma esitlusarvutisse\n"
"2. Lubage OpenLPis Remote-pistikprogramm (Seaded вҶ’ Seadista OpenLP вҶ’ Pistikprogrammid)\n"
"3. Lubage OpenLPis Alerts-pistikprogramm teatiste kuvamise toetamiseks\n"
"4. MГӨrkige Гјles OpenLP-arvuti IP-aadress\n"
"5. Sisestage serveri URL formaadis: http://IP_AADRESS:4316\n"
"6. Kui olete OpenLPis autentimise seadistanud, sisestage kasutajanimi ja parool"

